1
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:09,840
This is the Tianshu Medicine Array.

2
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:11,880
That's right.

3
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:14,200
He still needs to inject magic power into these formations.

4
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,079
This is the greatest protection

5
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,760
he can give your entire city.

6
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:19,680
Right,

7
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,120
Master?

8
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,040
Don't call me Master.

9
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,920
Brother Qingxuan.

10
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:37,920
I only know this Tianshu Medicine Array is a closely guarded secret.

11
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:40,720
I've only heard its name but don't know the details.

12
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,720
To see it today

13
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,120
is the honor of a lifetime.

14
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,560
Thank you, Master.

15
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,520
You can rest here first.

16
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,920
We'll go look for the materials right away.

17
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,320
I shall take my leave now.

18
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:55,520
Let me know if you need anything.

19
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,040
It is dangerous here,

20
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,120
and the matter in Ercheng

21
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,960
has nothing to do with you anyway.

22
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,920
You'd better leave as soon as possible.

23
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:10,120
I'm not leaving. I want to follow you, Master,

24
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,120
to slay demons.

25
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,240
Slay demons?

26
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,440
Do you think that with your broken bow,

27
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:18,440
you can defeat that kind of great demon?

28
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,320
She has lived for thousands of years.

29
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,880
I don't care if she's an old hag who's lived for hundreds

30
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,280
or thousands of years.

31
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,360
Old hag?

32
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:31,680
Master, please teach me.

33
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,060
I want to do my part too.

34
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,579
What about you?

35
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,120
Me?

36
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,200
I have nothing else to do anyway.

37
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:47,800
If I can protect the people of Ercheng with Brother Qingxuan,

38
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,660
it can be considered accumulating some good karma.

39
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,140
Whatever you want.

40
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,920
I'm going back to rest.

41
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,730
Have a good rest, ancestor.

42
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,200
Sister Gesang,

43
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,330
so he's willing to teach me, right?

44
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:08,880
I couldn't tell.

45
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,770
Little brother,

46
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:16,240
you were exceptionally brave today.

47
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:18,120
Have you never learned spells before?

48
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:20,380
I haven't. I've only practiced archery.

49
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,920
I usually hunt wild game

50
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,880
to provide food for the village.

51
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,120
Then you must follow my ancestor

52
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,180
and practice hard.

53
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:35,320
In time, you will surely achieve greatness.

54
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,120
Lord Hu really has a good eye.

55
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,880
I think so too.

56
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:38,880
You think so too?

57
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:39,720
That's great.

58
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,940
You need to practice hard.

59
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,050
Then I'll go back to my room to rest.

60
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:49,720
Don't come to me even if you need something.

61
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,000
Rest early, Lord Hu.

62
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,280
I beg for an answer.

63
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:23,440
What is the origin of the owner of this hair?

64
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,450
The reincarnation of an immortal.

65
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,050
The reincarnation of an immortal?

66
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,020
Banished to the mortal realm?

67
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:33,680
No.

68
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:39,400
What's his story with Qingxuan?

69
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,760
What's their specific connection?

70
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,000
I cannot say.

71
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,320
Then what was his name as an immortal?

72
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,600
Bai Jingqing.

73
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,920
Bai Jingqing.

74
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,120
That sounds

75
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:02,040
like a woman's name.

76
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,600
Master,

77
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,360
it's me, Hu San.

78
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,920
Master, I have something to report.

79
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,120
Can I come in and talk?

80
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,360
Come in.

81
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,440
Master,

82
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:38,920
today I saw you put a spell

83
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,380
on Feilu's bow and arrows.

84
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:42,400
But he has never practiced magic before.

85
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:45,200
The power of this arrow is extraordinary.

86
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,000
I actually think

87
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,560
that mortals

88
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,010
can also be destined

89
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,900
to be blessed by other spiritual powers,

90
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,280
borrowing external forces.

91
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,580
This world is vast,

92
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,360
with all kinds of phenomena.

93
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,840
Everything happens for a reason.

94
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:04,080
Feilu's bow can have such power.

95
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,300
It seems beyond common sense,

96
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,730
but if you investigate its origin,

97
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:11,680
it is also within the creation of heaven and earth.

98
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,920
My ancestors were indeed right.

99
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,160
This flying deer

100
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,240
is indeed extraordinary.

101
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,400
It came from the heavens.

102
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:29,100
You can observe the world.

103
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:34,000
Have you cultivated the Heavenly Eye?

104
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,120
No.

105
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,380
You couldn't have.

106
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:47,380
Those who cultivate the Heavenly Eye

107
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,900
can observe the return of spiritual energy,

108
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:52,280
see the changes in Yin, Yang, and the Five Elements,

109
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,920
perceive the true forms of immortals, gods, ghosts, and demons,

110
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,800
and see fate and reincarnation.

111
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,320
This is beyond ordinary people.

112
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,120
You are just a third-grade warlock.

113
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,060
You couldn't have.

114
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,280
Naturally, I can't do it.

115
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,440
But,

116
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:12,640
our Bureau of Astronomy has always had the right to observe the heavens,

117
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:16,840
and we possess ancient artifacts to seek divine answers.

118
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,680
So,

119
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:20,330
what did this divine artifact of yours

120
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,520
tell you exactly?

121
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:30,440
It said,

122
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,240
"Heaven's secrets must not be revealed."

123
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,970
So it didn't say anything else.

124
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,280
But ancestor.

125
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,160
Do you know

126
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:49,080
a High Immortal named Bai Jingqing?

127
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,360
Bai Jingqing.

128
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,120
High God.

129
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:11,820
Why are you here again?

130
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,040
You remember me, High God.

131
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:20,940
I wonder if the High God has found a way

132
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:23,450
to refuse severing the seven emotions

133
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:26,620
and still reach the Nine Heavens to become an immortal?

134
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,240
There are many cultivators in the world.

135
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:32,170
Those who have the fate to come here

136
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,800
are very few.

137
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,600
You have a deep affinity with immortality.

138
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,600
In just 500 years,

139
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,720
I have seen you twice.

140
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:43,640
But you gave up the path to immortality to keep your emotions.

141
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:44,600
Ridiculous.

142
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,200
What a pity.

143
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,920
I have an appointment with someone.

144
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,440
And now...

145
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:52,840
What about now?

146
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,800
Above the immortal steps,

147
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:57,440
do you think coming and going in my Sanshan School is child's play?

148
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,240
No, High God.

149
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:58,960
I just...

150
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,280
Your mind is unclear,

151
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,920
and your senses are not pure.

152
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:05,450
You'd better go back and cultivate for another thousand years.

153
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,680
Then can I stay here for a few days

154
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,520
to comprehend Taoism

155
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,600
and also

156
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,400
accompany you, High God?

157
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:20,080
This is a place for cultivating immortality.

158
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,340
How can I let a monster like you stay here?

159
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,600
Leave now.

160
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:42,240
Then I shall leave this lingering thought of longing.

161
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,610
A lingering thought of longing

162
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:49,480
can help me survive the cold.

163
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:56,090
What kind of obsession is it

164
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:59,400
that makes you waver about becoming an immortal?

165
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,860
If you speak of obsession,

166
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,400
there is only one.

167
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,520
Do you know

168
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:17,050
that a great disaster is coming to you?

169
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,610
A great disaster is coming?

170
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,280
Why do you say that, High God?

171
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,340
I truly do not understand.

172
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:28,200
You have traveled back and forth to Sanshanliu many times

173
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,730
and left just as many times.

174
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:32,600
Such behavior has long violated the Heavenly Dao.

175
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,920
If this time

176
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:38,000
you still refuse to sever your emotions

177
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,460
and insist on leaving,

178
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,040
then...

179
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,400
Then what?

180
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,250
You will lose all your cultivation

181
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,240
and revert to your original form.

182
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,520
And for all eternity,

183
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:52,930
you will never set foot on the path to immortality again.

184
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:58,720
Ping Jieqiang, Hai Hui.
